    "description": "Nestled within the Sidra sub-community in Dubai Hills Estate, this full -upgraded five-bedroom villa has been extended, adding a dining area and converting four bedrooms to five. Spanning 4,628 sq.ft., it showcases interiors with contemporary hues and clean lines.\n\nThe open-plan receptions offers a formal and an informal seating area, partially separated dining room, and a beautiful front kitchen supported by a secondary kitchen \u2014 both of them appointed with Miele appliances. The two kitchens were also a feature of the thoughtful extension.\n\nFull-height windows bathe the interiors with plenty of light, while extending the living spaces with the vast backyard. This rear garden comes complete with landscaping, a relaxing pool, seating area, and a shaded area with comprehensive dining setup and summer kitchen.\n\nThe bedrooms are all en-suite and conceived as tranquil escapes, with built-in wardrobes adding functionality. A maid\u2019s room and parking for two cars complete this stunning haven.\n\nResidents benefit from a host of the community\u2019s lifestyle amenities, including its many parks, Dubai Hills Golf Club, cycle tracks, Dubai Hills Mall, restaurants, cafes, dog parks, adult community pool, children's pool and play area, and community gym. Its proximity to some of the city\u2019s leading schools and hospitals positions it as a highly family-friendly community.\n\nExtremely well connected, Dubai Hills Estate, sits conveniently close to Downtown Dubai and Mall of the Emirates (15 minutes) Dubai Marina and Global Village (20 minutes), and DXB Airport (25 minutes).\n\nContact us to book a private viewing of this remarkable Sidra villa.",
